{
  "stem": "18626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 278.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But by the same Soviet army was chasing him and they didn't know how to run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were laying in the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I saw both sides, but it took three and a half years of punishment, killed out plenty Jews, till they saw what a change it was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, went back home from my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went back to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to my mother what I just saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's exactly like our papa said, our father said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Exactly what he was saying, it's happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother couldn't stop crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About my father's fate, I learned almost nine months later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A man was released from the ninth fortress where all the Jews from the-- from Slobodka, Kaunas, they're all taken to the Seventh Fort, sorry, not the Ninth, Seventh fortress.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all taken from the streets and from their homes, from [INAUDIBLE], Slobodka-- taken all to the Seventh Fort to be killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of my father's friends, he was a cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his name was Melamed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in that fort.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a friend, a Lithuanian, he took part of killing, you know, with the other Lithuanians, the Jews, was a friend with that Jew, Melamed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He built for him furniture a lot of times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to him before, shooting, you know, groups of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ways that they do to killing is groups, you know, like 50 at a time, or 30.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was almost at the grave to be shot, that Lithuanian partisan-- we called them partisans, the Lithuanians because they acted like partisans, you know, against the Russians and against the-- against the Russians of course.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He recognized he says, Melamed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
